{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-topic-js","path":"/zh/topic/vaccinations","result":{"data":{"contentfulTopic":{"title":"疫苗接種","content":{"content":"\n某些致命感染症，例如小兒麻痺、麻疹和肺炎，可藉由接種疫苗加以預防。洗手、乾淨的水、公共衛生和營養無法預防所有的感染症，尤其是空氣中的病菌。[^83]\n\n染上這類疾病可造成嚴重併發症，例如麻痺、先天缺陷、肝癌、肺炎和死亡。[^83]\n\n嬰兒和幼兒無法抵抗這類疾病，因為他們的免疫系統還不成熟。我們會在他們染病之\n施打疫苗，來預防他們染上這些疾病。[^83]\n\n成人則會因為年齡、糖尿病等健康狀況、生活型態和旅遊，而有較高的感染症發生風險.[^83]\n\n請準時施打一般建議使用的疫苗，來保護自己、親人和您的社區。請就您的疫苗接種詢問您的健康照護者。[^83]\n\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mLHnUjhzv9E\" class=\"embedly-card\" data-card-width=\"100%\" data-card-controls=\"0\">Embedded content: https://youtu.be/mLHnUjhzv9E</a>\n\n[美國衛生及公共服務部提供的「疫苗接種資訊」](https://www.vaccines.gov/index.html)\n\n[美國衛生及公共服務部提供的「嬰兒、兒童與青少年用疫苗](https://www.vaccines.gov/who_and_when/infants_to_teens/index.html)\n\n[美國衛生及公共服務部提供的「成人用疫苗」](https://www.vaccines.gov/who_and_when/adults/index.html)\n\n[美國衛生及公共服務部提供的 孕婦用疫苗](https://www.vaccines.gov/who_and_when/pregnant/index.html)\n\n[^83]: U.S. Department of Health & Human Services. Vaccines & Immunizations. https://www.vaccines.gov/index.html. Accessed April 8, 2018. Updated February 16, 2021.\n ↩\n"},"hero":{"file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/xbvvg00rroa3/4C5lHOe5qxjvY9PrhyerMF/ab5b39580879de4d5f176288b595bcd7/Cropped-Vaccinations.gif","fileName":"Cropped-Vaccinations.gif","contentType":"image/gif"}},"slug":"vaccinations"}},"pageContext":{"id":"24448783-72b6-576f-9086-3e32ffdd293d","icon":"injection","title":"疫苗接種","subtitle":"感染防疫","categories":["before-the-hospital","in-the-hospital","after-the-hospital"],"node_locale":"zh-Hant-TW","slug":"vaccinations","contentful_id":"KXpnB5WcG4AOIUiagc2gm","test":"test","translations":[{"node":{"id":"19346075-e966-5396-858b-3308292da387","icon":"injection","title":"Vaccinations","subtitle":"Infection Prevention","categories":["before-the-hospital","in-the-hospital","after-the-hospital"],"node_locale":"en-US","slug":"vaccinations","contentful_id":"KXpnB5WcG4AOIUiagc2gm"}},{"node":{"id":"78783f62-0a64-5293-ade8-37c89